values:
Never mix Lipton Lemon Ice Tea with milk... ever.
Tastebuds confused, like rancid milk + fresh, sweet-tasting lemonade.
For a while I was -almost- curious enough to add raw eggs and tons of sugar in it, mixed with chocolate milk to see how horrible it would taste like. Then my conscience kicked me in the balls and dragged me out of temporary insanity ^^;
